[[File:1897-1900 2c stamp of Seychelles.jpg|thumbnail|right|An 1897 stamp of Seychelles of the type held in the Archives.]] The '''Seychelles National Archives''' is the [[national archive]] of [[Seychelles]] and is located in [[Mahé, Seychelles|Mahé]]. Their mission is to "collect, preserve and make accessible archival documents of enduring value through the use of the latest information technology."<ref>[http://www.sna.gov.sc/about-us.aspx About Us] Seychelles National Archives, 2012. Retrieved 29 November 2013.</ref>
It was officially created in 1964.<ref>[http://www.sna.gov.sc/our-history.aspx Our history]</ref>
